<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Erkinger von Seinsheim</head><p>Der Rat kündigt Hans Maurer, Diener der Stadt, wegen der zu Langenfeld beschlagnahmten Waren an.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_39" id="19v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_39_r2l24">eidem </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_39_r2l25"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Erk<ex>inger</ex></expan> vvir <expan>ſende<ex>n</ex></expan> cʒu euch hanſen <expan>Mawr<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>dıen<ex>er</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_39_r2l26"><expan>cʒurede<ex>n</ex></expan> von der habe <expan>wege<ex>n</ex></expan> Als Jr den <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>n</expan> <expan>yecʒ<ex>unden</ex></expan> cʒu </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_39_r2l27">Langenfelt <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> habt vnd <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_39_r2l28"><expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> vt <expan>ſup<ex>ra</ex></expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_39" id="19v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Eidem </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Erk<ex>inger,</ex></expan> wir <expan>sende<ex>n</ex></expan> czu
                        euch Hansen <expan>Mawr<ex>er,</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>dien<ex>er,</ex></expan>
<expan>czu rede<ex>n</ex></expan> von der habe
                            <expan>wege<ex>n,</ex></expan> als ir den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>yecz<ex>unden</ex></expan> czu Langenfelt
                            <expan>aufgehalte<ex>n</ex></expan> habt. Und
                            <expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                <expan>sup<ex>ra.</ex></expan>
</ab>
</div>
